{
  "name": "01 - Process new DJ request",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "Workflow 01: every minute read Google Sheet rows, process only rows with empty status, normalize with native OpenAI node, search Spotify by spotify_query and fallback AI_title, dedupe/score all tracks, update the matched row by Sygnatura czasowa. This workflow does not add anything to a Spotify playlist.",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "0f5cf2e4-3dd1-4ae5-81da-0a2ec9341b9a",
      "name": "README - workflow scope",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1180,
        -360
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "Required placeholders:\n- __GOOGLE_SPREADSHEET_ID__\n- __REQUESTS_SHEET_NAME__\n- __GOOGLE_SHEETS_CREDENTIAL_NAME__\n- __OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_NAME__\n- __SPOTIFY_CREDENTIAL_NAME__\n\nRows are matched and updated by the physical Google Form column: Sygnatura czasowa. Empty status means the row is new and ready to process.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "e4b6fd7d-9ced-4837-b182-b281d1dfc646",
